title: Sky (SKY) Gets Listed on Bitunix!
content: Dear Bitunix Users, Bitunix has completed to token swap from Maker (MKR) to Sky (SKY). And Sky(SKY) is getting listed on Bitunix. The supported trading pair will be SKY/USDT on the spot market. Deposit & WithdrawalDeposits Effective ImmediatelyWithdrawal: 08:00 on August 25, 2025 (UTC) Spot TradingSpot trading for SKY/USDT will start at 08:00 on August 25, 2025 (UTC). Project IntroductionSky (SKY)Sky (SKY) is the governance token of a decentralized protocol offering non-custodial stablecoin savings, rewards, and staking features, evolved from MakerDAO’s ecosystem. Sky Protocol focuses on decentralized finance (DeFi) tools for saving, earning rewards, and governance. Its USDS stablecoin (upgraded from DAI) powers features like the Sky Savings Rate (4.5% annual yield) and Sky Token Rewards, where users earn SKY by supplying USDS. The protocol emphasizes non-custodial control, allowing users to retain ownership of assets while accessing yields.Official Website: https://sky.money/ Blockchain Explorer: https://etherscan.io/address/0x56072c95faa701256059aa122697b133aded9279  Regards, Bitunix TeamAugust 25, 2025 Join Bitunix Community:X: https://X.com/bitunixofficial Telegram: https://t.me/bitunixglobalFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/bitunixInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/bitunixofficial  *Risk Warning:The cryptocurrency market is available worldwide 24 x 7 for trading with no market close or open times.
